Title: Sample Script
Author: ReelWalia Test

INT. COFFEE SHOP - DAY

A busy morning. MAYA (30s, sharp blazer) waits in line.

MAYA
Double espresso, please.

BARISTA
Coming right up.

EXT. CITY STREET - NIGHT

Rain slicks the pavement. Maya hurries under an awning, phone in hand.

MAYA
(into phone)
I'm five minutes out.

INT. MAYA'S APARTMENT - LATER

Maya kicks off wet shoes and collapses on the couch.

MAYA
What a day.
